Final Fantasy 7 Items.

Text file containing development notes about the items being added.

Mythril Items:
	> Ingot - Used to craft the basic weapons, Mythril Pole and Mythril Claw Blades. Smelted from Mythril Ore blocks.
	> Pole - Replacement for sticks in crafting.
	> Claw Blade - Used for certain crafting.

Elemental Crystals:
	> Fire
	> Water
	> Earth
	> Air
		All crystals used for crafting Materia purposes. Dropped by mining relevant Elemental Ores.

No particular information needed.